# dogfood.scenarios — TRACKING file, deliberately separate from
# core.scenarios (the gating suite). Encodes the real dogfood line of
# 2026-07-15 replayed raw, keystroke for keystroke:
#
#   typed:    "Lyklaborð sem.er alveg fara lega hratt og giskar a allt fer
#              sem naður awgke. Hmmm ik - ekki að virka aveg nogg."
#   intended: "Lyklaborð sem er alveg fáránlega hratt og giskar á allt fer
#              sem maður <awgke = mash junk>. Hmmm ok - ekki að virka
#              alveg nógu."
#
# Run:  swift run -c release type-repl run Scenarios/dogfood.scenarios
#
# Current contract (fixes 1-3 applied end to end):
#   fix 1  "sem.er"  → "sem er"   (dotted space-miss escape, auto-applied)
#   fix 2  "fara lega" was typed as TWO valid words around a real spacebar
#          tap — nothing to correct at replay time; the fix guarantees no
#          false split ever auto-applies over a "fáránlega"-class repair
#          (core.scenarios "faralega …" locks that)
#   fix 3  "a" → "á"              (single-letter accent restoration, IS lane)
#   fix 4  "naður" stays (valid; "maður" offered in the bar — core suite)
#   fix 5  "aveg"/"nogg"/"ik" stay (offers locked in core + eval; margins
#          deliberately keep them tap-only), "awgke" stays (mash junk)
#
# ASPIRATIONAL (cannot pass under the sacred conservatism rules — valid
# words are never auto-replaced, and typed-with-a-real-space tokens commit
# as typed; kept here as the north star for the touch-decoder wave):
#   EXPECT_BUFFER "Lyklaborð sem er alveg fáránlega hratt og giskar á allt fer sem maður awgke. Hmmm ok - ekki að virka alveg nógu. "

LIMIT 5

SCENARIO dogfood line 2026-07-15 replayed raw
T "Lyklaborð sem.er alveg fara lega hratt og giskar a allt fer sem naður awgke. Hmmm ik - ekki að virka aveg nogg. "
EXPECT_BUFFER "Lyklaborð sem er alveg fara lega hratt og giskar á allt fer sem naður awgke. Hmmm ik - ekki að virka aveg nogg. "

