# ============================================================================
# Session 2026-07-16T22-45-30 — personal-learning self-poisoning (wave 26)
# ============================================================================
# Two systemic leaks: (1) lazy acute-less commits (þvi, gret) get learned
# and then, as "valid personal vocabulary", veto the restoration autocorrect
# they were produced by — the more you rely on restoration, the faster it
# dies; (2) iOS sentence-start autocaps get learned into surfaces ("Fyrir",
# "Frábær") that then title-case every mid-sentence correction. Fix: an
# IMPLICITLY learned pure acute-fold shadow of a dominant base word loses
# the autocorrect veto (keeps ranking/prediction boosts — its counts ride
# on the restored twin); a leading-cap surface of common base vocabulary
# keeps the pipeline casing. Explicit adds / verbatim taps / tombstones
# keep full veto power; OOV surfaces stay byte-exact.

